E","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"800","height":"450","altText":"Picture of x-ray machine coloured bule with sharp object through the middle","caption":"Lorde","photographer":"Frontier Touring","copyright":"Frontier Touring","sequenceNumber":"100"},{"marketVariantId":"","multimediaId":"68771223260ed53b07d34514","authoredDate":"2025-07-16","serverPath":"https://assets.atdw-online.com.au/images/c967b7e8303b5ea420d1cda313706a62.jpeg?rect=0%2C150%2C1600%2C900&w=280&h=158&rot=360&q=eyJ0eXBlIjoibGlzdGluZyIsImxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjY4NzcxMGU2ZDRmY2Y3MzYxYTdkNWE3YyIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"280","height":"158","altText":"Picture of x-ray machine coloured bule with sharp object through the middle","caption":"Lorde","photographer":"Frontier Touring","copyright":"Frontier Touring","sequenceNumber":"100"}],"openTimes":[],"productComments":[{"marketVariantId":"English / Global","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ENGLISH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"English","commentText":"Frontier Touring is ecstatic to announce global alt-pop icon, Lorde, will bring her highly anticipated Ultrasound World Tour to her home country New Zealand and Australia in February 2026!\n\nThe Ultrasound World Tour will be Lorde's first New Zealand and Australian shows since 2023's Solar Power Tour."},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"Frontier Touring se complace en anunciar que Lorde ícono mundial del pop alternativo, llevará su esperadísima gira mundial Ultrasound a su país natal, Nueva Zelanda, y a Australia en febrero de 2026.\n\nLa gira mundial Ultrasound será la primera de Lorde en Nueva Zelanda y Australia desde su gira Solar Power de 2023."},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"A Frontier Touring tem o prazer de anunciar que o ícone global do alt-pop, Lorde, trará sua aguardada Ultrasound World Tour para seu país natal, Nova Zelândia, e Austrália, em fevereiro de 2026!\n\nA Ultrasound World Tour será o primeiro show de Lorde na Nova Zelândia e Austrália desde a Solar Power Tour, de 2023."},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Frontier Touring est ravi d'annoncer que Lorde, icône mondiale de la pop alternative, présentera sa tournée mondiale très attendue Ultrasound World Tour en Nouvelle-Zélande et en Australie, son pays d'origine, en février 2026 !\n\nL'Ultrasound World Tour sera le premier concert de Lorde en Nouvelle-Zélande et en Australie depuis la tournée Solar Power Tour de 2023."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Frontier Touring freut sich, bekannt zu geben, dass die weltweite Alt-Pop-Ikone Lorde ihre mit Spannung erwartete Ultrasound World Tour im Februar 2026 in ihr Heimatland Neuseeland und nach Australien bringt!\n\nDie Ultrasound World Tour ist Lordes erste Show in Neuseeland und Australien seit ihrer Solar Power Tour 2023."},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Frontier Touring è entusiasta di annunciare che Lorde, icona mondiale dell'alt-pop, porterà il suo attesissimo Ultrasound World Tour nel suo paese d'origine, la Nuova Zelanda, e in Australia a febbraio 2026!\n\nL'Ultrasound World Tour sarà il primo concerto di Lorde in Nuova Zelanda e Australia dal Solar Power Tour del 2023."},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"프론티어 투어링(Frontier Touring)은 세계적인 얼터너티브 팝 아이콘인 로드(Lorde)가 2026년 2월 고국 뉴질랜드와 호주에서 많은 기대를 모은 '울트라사운드 월드 투어(Ultrasound World Tour)'를 개최한다는 소식을 전하게 되어 매우 기쁩니다!\n\n울트라사운드 월드 투어는 로드가 2023년 '솔라 파워 투어(Solar Power Tour)' 이후 처음으로 뉴질랜드와 호주에서 공연하는 투어입니다."},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Frontier Touring dengan bangga mengumumkan bahwa ikon alt-pop global, Lorde, akan menggelar Ultrasound World Tour yang sangat dinantikan di negara asalnya, Selandia Baru, dan Australia, pada Februari 2026!\n\nUltrasound World Tour akan menjadi pertunjukan pertama Lorde di Selandia Baru dan Australia sejak Solar Power Tour tahun 2023."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"Frontier Touring 欣喜地宣布，全球另类流行偶像 Lorde 将于 2026 年 2 月，带着她备受期待的“超声波世界巡回演唱会”来到她的祖国新西兰和澳大利亚！\n\n“超声波世界巡回演唱会”将是 Lorde 自 2023 年“太阳能巡回演唱会”以来首次在新西兰和澳大利亚演出。"},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"Frontier Touringは、世界的なオルタナティブ・ポップ・アイコン、ロードが、2026年2月に母国ニュージーランドとオーストラリアで、待望の「ウルトラサウンド・ワールドツアー」を開催することを発表いたします！\n\n「ウルトラサウンド・ワールドツアー」は、ロードにとって2023年の「ソーラー・パワー・ツアー」以来となるニュージーランドとオーストラリアでの公演となります。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"Frontier Touring 很高興地宣布，全球另類流行偶像 Lorde 將於 2026 年 2 月，帶著她備受期待的“超音波世界巡迴演唱會”來到她的祖國新西蘭和澳大利亞！\n\n「超音波世界巡迴演唱會」將是 Lorde 自 2023 年「太陽能巡迴演唱會」以來首次在新西蘭和澳洲演出。"}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"Brisbane Entertainment Centre","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"1 Melaleuca Drive","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Boondall","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4034","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.3422784","geocodeGdaLongitude":"153.0706395","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationsh